name: Berada Di Jalan (Indehoj Di Atas Motor)
description:
The weekend is here, everyone wants to have fun. Strolling into the city center from day to night is something fun. Especially taking your partner around the city on a motorbike.

Basic work using Chinese ink on paper and then working through digital media.
